{"tid":662785,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"PC Steam將推手機遊玩功能 5月下旬對應Android‧iOS手機","createTime":"2018-05-12T17:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T10:56:30.000Z","uid":119778,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca043d23377b0275eb44937380b4c32fda6956ae","tid":662785,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"智能手機娛樂已經佔據大部分玩家時間，似乎大家都不想再於電腦及遊戲主機玩遊戲，PC Steam平台剛宣佈會加強手機平台支援，稍後推出手機連線App，可以在手機及平板電腦等設備使用Steam遊戲庫及串流影像功能。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2070000/2070336/20180510_wes_steam_3_600.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2070000%2F2070336%2F20180510_wes_steam_3_600.jpg%20&h=378cd742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2070000/2070336/20180510_wes_steam_2_600.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2070000%2F2070336%2F20180510_wes_steam_2_600.jpg%20&h=ea1a0ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPC Steam是電腦最大的遊戲平台，近年也積極擴展功能，將PC GAME帶出電腦以外，如串流盒及控制器等，改善ＰＣ遊戲體驗。目前Steam對應的串流功能，僅對應家居網絡環境，使用Windows筆電或STEAM串流盒，連線到ＰＣ主機上以執行遊戲。官方宣佈將在５月２１日起，在Android手機、平板電腦、電視，以及iOS手機、平板電腦、Apple TV推出Steam Link App，經由有線或5GHz無線網絡連接PC主機，體驗遊戲庫的內容，並可以對應Steam控制器、MFI控制器等輸入方式。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Steam平台目前亦有愈來愈多的影像內容，官方表示今後預定夏天左右，會推出Steam Video App，針對Wi-Fi及LTE流動網絡環境，在Android及iOS裝置提供串流影像服務，以及離線觀看功能。"},{"pid":"72b141ef67223fb0b2bc677f0581e5611ae4e35e","tid":662785,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"淨係玩到啲小遊戲咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8864efa53dd3b7f8872971cf659d993f211cf8","tid":662785,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T17:05:48.000Z","msg":"串流最啱就係用嚟玩音樂或者動作遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebe56cae7939427d7ba62f71a328c47c19e7d44","tid":662785,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T03:36:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4891671f9bca64fccbf116e9bff17230995104b6","tid":662785,"uid":23764,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/163359_96a1bd32140c55646a4a522254248fe1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F163359_96a1bd32140c55646a4a522254248fe1.png&h=ab93fd7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實要焗住買個steam controller,除非你諗住帶keyboard 滑鼠出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f1fc9eab6e6ce92188a48724f0a1df21eb33a5","tid":662785,"uid":18082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4891671f9bca64fccbf116e9bff17230995104b6","tid":662785,"uid":23764,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/163359_96a1bd32140c55646a4a522254248fe1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F163359_96a1bd32140c55646a4a522254248fe1.png&h=ab93fd7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實要焗住買個steam controller,除非你諗住帶keyboard 滑鼠出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"情願買個電話用既都唔用佢自家果款"},{"pid":"c6a0a01e7b1505e1e95a6524019661ff0f1b8587","tid":662785,"uid":71484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T10:15:42.000Z","msg":"即係玩到有出pc同手機平台嘅game?<br />\n係就即刻入手解密謎game bundle"},{"pid":"60a13c07b8fb82832a6ae9c710f8418ca377ef24","tid":662785,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f1fc9eab6e6ce92188a48724f0a1df21eb33a5","tid":662785,"uid":18082,"like":0,"